								"paragraphOrdinal": 1,
								"paragraphTitle":  "The Open University",
								"paragraphSubtitles": null,
								"paragraphContents": [
									"It’s never too late to learn something new. The Open University is the largest university in the UK, with almost 174,000 students in 2015/2016 alone. It is a distance learning university, and it’s for anyone who wants to study and learn a new skill."
								]
							},
							{
								"paragraphOrdinal": 2,
								"paragraphTitle": "FAQs",
								"paragraphSubtitles": ["Who are the courses for?" ],
								"paragraphContents": [
									"Open University degree courses are open for anyone. Many people who have jobs or cannot go to a normal university on weekdays choose to study with us. As a distance learning university, it’s perfect for anyone who wants to study from home."
								]
							},
							{
								"paragraphOrdinal": 3,
								"paragraphTitle": "How much does it cost?",
								"paragraphSubtitles": null,
								"paragraphContents": [
									"The cost of full-time study is almost half that of other universities in the UK."
								]
							},
							{
								"paragraphOrdinal": 4,
								"paragraphTitle": "What subjects do you teach?",
								"paragraphSubtitles": null,
								"paragraphContents": [ 
									"There are nearly 500 courses to choose from."
								]
							},
							{
								"paragraphOrdinal": 5,
								"paragraphTitle": "When do students go to classes?",
								"paragraphSubtitles": null,
								"paragraphContents": [ 
									"Students don’t ‘go’ to classes. All of the classes and resources are available online or through print and video sources, so students can access them when they need to."
								]
							},
							{
								"paragraphOrdinal": 6,
								"paragraphTitle": "Where do students meet their teachers?",
								"paragraphSubtitles": null,
								"paragraphContents": [ 
									"They don’t. Students usually send homework to their teachers. The teachers reply by email."
								]
							},	
							{
								"paragraphOrdinal": 7,
								"paragraphTitle": "How long does an average degree course take?",
								"paragraphSubtitles": null,
								"paragraphContents": [ 
									"It takes an average of six years for most students to finish their degrees."
								]
							},	
							{
								"paragraphOrdinal": 8,
								"paragraphTitle": "Why do people take distance learning courses?",
								"paragraphSubtitles": null,
								"paragraphContents": [ 
									"A lot of people work during the day and study in their free time. The Open University is flexible. You can study anywhere, anytime"
								]
							}		
